msgid "Sincere service, innovative communication, mutual success."
msgstr "Layanan tulus, komunikasi inovatif, kesuksesan bersama."

msgid "Your trusted partner for comprehensive marine equipment supply, technical solutions and ship services in Indonesia."
msgstr "Mitra terpercaya Anda untuk pasokan peralatan kelautan, solusi teknis, dan layanan kapal di Indonesia."

msgid "Patented static frequency converter technology, reducing fuel consumption by 20%+ while ships are docked."
msgstr "Teknologi konverter frekuensi statis yang dipatenkan, mengurangi konsumsi bahan bakar 20%+ saat kapal berlabuh."

